{"tid":1450113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武力升級，文宣進場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:46:51.000Z","uid":239496,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d30edef9b2b8d3e345916299a670ee90578f5c1a","tid":1450113,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"依家係翻版64啊<br />\n我地要文宣強調我地武力升級嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">合理性</span></span><br />\n係中央同林政容許警黑合作<br />\n係中央挑起戰爭<br />\n係中央破壞一國兩制<br />\n係中央破壞社會秩序<br />\n係中央目無法紀<br />\n係中央草菅人命<br />\n係中央令到香港天怒人怨 生靈塗炭<br />\n然後我地要升級<br />\n<br />\n記住唔好今日係機場唔好先郁手<br />\n唔好被旅客挑釁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果遇到黑警驅趕及放催淚彈</span></span><br />\n我要機場全部人圍毆佢哋！死都要圍毆佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeLdo1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeLdo1x.jpg&h=29a3d590&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3155a55078541bb0567c8898a66dc25850d5d72","tid":1450113,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"98851aff2e0203dc864aa35e2ce3a4dec07bb217","tid":1450113,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"唔識起標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b28bbaeb003d5c433d45b82ad4491cf3cc1017","tid":1450113,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d0947d590e472c445df0db16b96d1c8101d9e3","tid":1450113,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"血債血償<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05